<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">An air carrier shall provide safe and adequate interstate air transportation.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idcbc25afb-47c4-11f1-9671-b5c725212f70">(<ref href="/us/pl/103/272/s1/e">Pub. L. 103–272, § 1(e)</ref>, <date date="1994-07-05">July 5, 1994</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/108/1140">108 Stat. 1140</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
